Standard and Poor's Corp said it raisedto A from A-minus Bay State Gas Co's preferred stock.    S and P affirmed the company's A-rated senior debt and A-1commercial paper. Bay State has 75 mln dlrs of long-term debtand preferred outstanding.    The rating agency said its action mainly reflected debtredemptions. S and P also said the outlook for firm salesgrowth is positive because of a vibrant regional economy. Reuter&#3;